text: Powerful 7.1 earthquake strikes Philippines; at least 4 dead https://t.co/qx7ooH3HTK

Powerful earthquake of magnitude 7 strikes in #Philippines killed 4 person 60  injured and several buildings damaged through capital #Manila. Geological survey data of #USA at a shallow depth 10 km. rescue operation started  by @UNOCHA #Earhquake #World #Eu @UNOCHA_fr  #Indonesia https://t.co/3rSUj51G1j

Wounded residents because of the earthquake are being treated at the Abra Provincial Hospital.

DSWD says 64 are injured while 25 families have evacuated because of the earthquake.
